{"tid":1850800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦落命令 叫地區莊腳將冇口罩責任推比新任區議員","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T05:56:50.000Z","uid":232237,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5b784665ca411c566be6ddd741b7b17a47892b8d","tid":1850800,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:10:27.000Z","msg":"唔好問消息來源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母 又係局來既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點拆好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae255831e8fde449f23523eb43021d40476dd75","tid":1850800,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><